card.desc:
Plan releases on Spotify, Apple Music, etc.
Upload and Monetize Recordings

- Distribute your music on streaming services like Spotify, Apple Music, and Bandcamp.
- Promote new releases through social media and your website.
- Track streaming metrics and revenue.

Once tracks are ready, use a distribution service like DistroKid or TuneCore to get your music on streaming platforms. Promote each release with a coordinated social media campaign.

- Upload songs to streaming services (Spotify, Apple Music).
- Promote new releases on social media and your website.
- Monitor streaming analytics to gauge audience reception.
